{{Infobox dungeon |name = Ruins of Abundance |image = [[File:Ruins of Abundance.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Ruins of Abundance. |tokens = 1,200,000 |location = North of Haina Desert. }}
'''Ruins of Abundance''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Alola]]. It initially has 121 tiles arranged in a 11x11 square, including 11 chest tiles, 41 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 16,435,490 HP.
